title:
Medical software is any software item or system used within a medical context, such as:
standalone software used for diagnostic or therapeutic purposes;
software embedded in a medical device (often referred to as "medical device software");
software that drives a medical device or determines how it is used;
software that acts as an accessory to a medical device;
software used in the design, production, and testing of a medical device; or
software that provides quality control management of a medical device.Dynamic Energy Systems MedAct, Medical condition coding software, Medical procedure coding software, PracticeWorks Systems Kodak WINOMS CS, Healthcare common procedure coding system HCPCS, MEDITECH software, e-MDs Bill, Epic Systems, Allscripts Misys Healthcare Systems, Alteer Office, CareCentric MestaMed, Cerner ProFile, Electronic medical record EMR software, Emdeon HealthPro, GE Healthcare Centricity EMR, Henry Schein Dentrix, Kodak Dental Systems Kodak SOFTDENT Practice management software PMS, McKesson Horizon Ambulatory Care, MEDENT, MedFORCE Technologies WorkFLOW, MEDITECH Medical and Practice Management MPM Suite, Misys Healthcare Systems Misys Tiger, PCC EHR, PCC Pediatric Partner, Patient tracking software, PointClickCare HER, Electronic health record EHR software, Allscripts Professional EHR, Allscripts Sunrise Clinical Manager, Amkai AmkaiCharts, Bizmatics PrognoCIS EMR System, Cerner Millennium, Cerner PowerChart, ChartWare EMR, Computerized physician order entry CPOE software, e-MDs software, eClinicalWorks, Electronic medical administration record eMAR software, Healthcare management system, MEDITECH Healthcare Information System HCIS, Mediware ClosedLoop Clinical Systems, Mediware Information Systems MediCOE, Medscribbler Enterprise, MicroFour PracticeStudio.NET EMR, Netsmart Technologies CareNet, NextGen Healthcare Information Systems EMR, Picis CareSuite, Seimens Healthineers, SOAPware EMR, StatCom Patient Flow Logistics Enterprise Suite, SynaMed EMR, Texas Medical Software SpringCharts EMR, VISICU eICU Program, STAT! Systems QD Clinical, Allscripts, ADInstruments LabChart, Electromyograph analysis software, Gait analysis software, Instrument control software, Instrument validation software, Medical imaging software, Medical information software, Virtual instrument software, Computer Service & Support CLS-2000 Laboratory System, Orchard Software Orchard Harvest LIS, Plate reader 